== 2008年9月14日後的一週 ==
=== 大型金融機構的危機 ===
{{參見|美國國際集團}}
9月14日星期日，[[雷曼兄弟|雷曼兄弟]]在[[美國聯準會|美國聯準會]]拒絕提供資金支持援助後提出破產申請，而在同一天[[美林证券|美林证券]]宣佈被[[美國銀行|美國銀行]]收購。這兩件事標誌著接下來這一星期[[2008年9月全球股市大崩盤|2008年9月全球股市大崩盤]]的序幕，在9月15日（星期一）和9月17日（星期三）全球股市發生市值暴跌的情形。在9月16日，[[美國國際集團|美國國際集團]]（[[AIG|AIG]]）因持有許多信用已經違約的到期合約而被調低其信用評級，該保險集團自身也陷入了一場清償危機（liquidity crisis）。在AIG證實其已經無法找到願意給它提供貸款、拯救它避免破產的出借人的情況下，[[聯準會|聯準會]]應AIG要求，向AIG提供高達850億美元的同業信貸融資便利服務（credit facility），條件是獲取AIG 79.9%的權益性資本（equity interest），并有權對之前已經發行的[[普通股|普通股]]、[[優先股|優先股]]暫停派發[[紅利|紅利]]或[[股息|股息]]。

=== 貨幣市場基金保險及禁止放空 ===
9月16日，金融市場上一家大型的共同基金[[Reserve_Primary_Fund|Reserve Primary Fund]]因為披露其持有雷曼兄弟公司的債券，其股價下跌至1美元以下，這導致投資者贖回他們的基金需求大幅擴散，金融危機進一步惡化<ref name='NYT-Bernard-2008-09-17'>[http://www.nytimes.com/2008/09/18/business/yourmoney/18money.html "Money Market Funds Enter a World of Risk"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/09/18/business/yourmoney/18money.html |date=20201128183133 }} article by Tara Siegel Bernard in ''[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] September 17, 2008</ref>。截至9月18日早晨，總市值為4兆美元的市場上，機構投資者要求“賣出”（sell orders）的交易訂單市值高達5千億美元，而[[美国联邦储备系统|美国联邦储备系统]]注入市場的流動性資金僅有1050億美元，此刻立即使市場崩解<ref name='NYPost-Gray-2008-09-18'>Gray, Michael. [http://www.nypost.com/seven/09212008/business/almost_armageddon_130110.htm "Almost Armageddon: Markets Were 500 Trades from a Meltdown] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nypost.com/seven/09212008/business/almost_armageddon_130110.htm |date=20090722101111 }}（September 21, 2008）[[New_York_Post|New York Post]]</ref>。

在9月19日，[[美國財政部|美國財政部]]提供暫時性的保險（akin to [[FDIC|FDIC]] insurance of bank accounts）向貨幣市場挹注資金<ref name='Treasury-Money Market Insurance-2008-09-18'>[http://www.treasury.gov/press/releases/hp1147.htm "Treasury Announces Guaranty Program for Money Market Funds"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.treasury.gov/press/releases/hp1147.htm |date=20090502114711 }}（September 19, 2008）Press Release. United States Department of the Treasury.</ref>。

到本周末，[[英國金融服務管理局|英國金融服務管理局]]（Financial Services Authority）、[[美國證券交易委員會|美國證券交易委員會]]暫停了對本國的金融類股票[[短線賣空|短線賣空]]交易<ref name='NYT-Bajaj-2008-09-20'>[http://www.nytimes.com/2008/09/20/business/20sec.html "S.E.C. Issues Temporary Ban on Short-Selling"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/09/20/business/20sec.html |date=20201128020738 }} article by Vikas Bajaj and Jonathan D. Glater in ''[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]'' September 19, 2008</ref>；其他國家的金融主管單位也採取了類似的因應措施<ref name="aus-09-22">{{cite news | title = Australian short selling ban goes further than other bourses | publisher = ''NBR'' | date = 2008-09-22 | url = http://www.nbr.co.nz/article/australian-short-selling-ban-goes-further-other-bourses-35494 | accessdate = 2008-09-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110927054436/http://www.nbr.co.nz/article/australian-short-selling-ban-goes-further-other-bourses-35494 | archive-date = 2011-09-27 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。市場信心也在財政部和美國證券交易管理委員會的努力及公關宣傳下得到了一定的恢復<ref>[http://www.nytimes.com/2008/09/20/business/economy/20cndleadall.html "Stocks Surge as U.S. Acts to Shore Up Money Funds and Limits Short Selling"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/09/20/business/economy/20cndleadall.html |date=20201128190315 }} article by Graham Bowley in ''[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]'' September 19, 2008</ref><ref>[http://www.nytimes.com/2008/09/20/washington/19cnd-cong.html "Congressional Leaders Were Stunned by Warnings"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/09/20/washington/19cnd-cong.html |date=20201128190330 }} article by David M. Herszenhorn in ''[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]'' September 19, 2008</ref>。

=== 美國救市方案 ===
{{main|2008年經濟穩定緊急法案}}
2008年9月19日，[[美國財政部長|美國財政部長]][[保爾森|保爾森]]公佈了一項法案計畫，以改善[[次級房屋信貸危機|次級房屋信貸危機]]所造成的經濟困境。他提出了[[問題資產解決方案|問題資產解決方案]]（之後整合在[[2008年經濟穩定緊急法案|2008年經濟穩定緊急法案]]中），將允許美國政府從金融機構購買有問題的[[流動資產|流動資產]]（又稱[[不良資產|不良資產]]）。<ref>[http://www.nytimes.com/2008/09/19/business/19fed.html "Vast Bailout by U.S. Proposed in Bid to Stem Financial Crisis"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/09/19/business/19fed.html |date=20201109032245 }} article by Edmund L. Andrews in ''[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]'' September 18, 2008</ref><ref>"[http://www.nytimes.com/2008/09/20/business/economy/20paulson.html Paulson Argues for Need to Buy Mortgages] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/09/20/business/economy/20paulson.html |date=20201109030113 }}" article by David Stout in ''[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]'' September 19, 2008</ref>

這項法案對美國金融安全保障方面的重要性而言，是相當難以確定的。<ref  name='NYT=Bjaj-2008-09-24'>[http://www.nytimes.com/2008/09/25/business/25value.html "Plan's Mystery: What's All This Stuff Worth?"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/09/25/business/25value.html |date=20201127234212 }} article by Vikas Bajaj in ''[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]'' September 24, 2008</ref>

在美國財政部長、[[美国联邦储备系统|美国联邦储备系统]]主席和[[美國證券交易委員會|美國證券交易委員會]]主席三者之間的協商會議當中，[[美國國會|美國國會]]主席和[[美國總統|美國總統]]提議出計畫，以進一步全面的解決金融機構不良資產所產生的問題。在週末前財政部長和總統[[乔治·沃克·布什|乔治·沃克·布什]]宣佈救市方案，內容包括政府撥出七千億美元來購買非流動的[[不動產擔保證券|不動產擔保證券]]，目的是增加[[次級貸款市場|次級貸款市場]]的流動性和減少擁有這些證券的金融機構可能會面對的虧損。此計劃的草案獲股市投資者的積極反應，挹注資金計劃的具體細節有待眾議院落實。<ref>[http://www.nytimes.com/2008/09/20/business/20fed.html "Bush Officials Urge Swift Action on Rescue Powers"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/09/20/business/20fed.html |date=20201128190251 }} article by Edmund L. Andrews in ''[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]'' September 19, 2008</ref><ref>[http://www.nytimes.com/2008/09/21/business/21draftcnd.html  Draft Proposal for Bailout Plan] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/09/21/business/21draftcnd.html |date=20201128190347 }}（September 21, 2008）. ''New York Times''</ref><ref>[http://www.nytimes.com/aponline/business/AP-Financial-Meltdown.html "Rescue Plan Seeks $700 Billion to Buy Bad Mortgages"] article by [[The_Associated_Press|The Associated Press]] in ''[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]'' September 20, 2008</ref><ref>[http://www.nytimes.com/2008/09/21/business/21cong.html "$700 Billion Is Sought for Wall Street in Vast Bailout"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/09/21/business/21cong.html |date=20201128190340 }} article by David M. Herszenhorn in ''[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]'' September 20, 2008</ref>

