ine.co.uk/tol/business/economics/article4888248.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>在10月6日德國總理[[梅克爾|安格拉·多羅特亞·梅克爾]]宣布政府會對德國私有銀行的所有存款進行保障。政府又宣佈一個挽救[[德國|德國]]借貸公司The Hypo Real Estate（HRE）的計劃。<ref>[[Deutsche_Welle|Deutsche Welle]]。[http://www.dw-world.de/dw/article/0,2144,3694172,00.html German Government Under Pressure to Deliver on Crisis Promise] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dw-world.de/dw/article/0,2144,3694172,00.html |date=20090114120306 }}（English）Retrieved 2008-10-06</ref><ref>[[Deutsche_Welle|Deutsche Welle]]。[http://www.dw-world.de/popups/popup_single_mediaplayer/0,,3692883_type_video_struct_1432,00.html?mytitle=Berlin%2Bhas%2BGiven%2Ba%2BBlanket%2BGuarantee%2Bfor%2Ball%2BPrivate%2BBank%2BSavings Berlin has Given a Blanket Guarantee for all Private Bank Savings] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dw-world.de/popups/popup_single_mediaplayer/0,,3692883_type_video_struct_1432,00.html?mytitle=Berlin%2Bhas%2BGiven%2Ba%2BBlanket%2BGuarantee%2Bfor%2Ball%2BPrivate%2BBank%2BSavings |date=20090114120532 }}.（English）Retrieved 2008-10-06.（video, English）Merkel: "we also pledge that those who have conducted business irresponsibly will be held to account. The government will ensure that that happens."</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/389588ae-93ce-11dd-9a63-0000779fd18c.html|title=Berlin shrugs off attacks on savings pledge|publisher=The Financial Times|date=2008-10-06|accessdate=2008-10-06|first=Bertrand|last=Benoitt|coauthors=George Parker|archive-date=2008-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081108201016/http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/389588ae-93ce-11dd-9a63-0000779fd18c.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>在同一日美國紐約的[[道瓊工業指數|道瓊工業指數]]重挫，在收盤時指數跌破了10,000點，即從2007年10月9日時的指數創下超過14,000點的高點時，所累積的跌幅為30%。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/10/07/business/07markets.html|title=Chaotic Day Ends With Stocks Off 3.8%|publisher=The New York Times|date=2008-10-06|accessdate=2008-10-06|first=Micheal M.|last=Grynbaum|coauthors=|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/